1
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,970
Your sister-in-law is really nice to you.

2
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,280
Really?

3
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:10,250
Where are you going?

4
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:14,960
Bai Qing.

5
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,080
I am truly sorry

6
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:18,880
that you got hurt because of me.

7
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:20,400
I truly apologize. I...

8
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,360
Su Wan.

9
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:23,300
Ever since I first met you,

10
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:25,200
I've envied you.

11
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,980
I envy that you go to a top university.

12
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,800
I envy your looks.

13
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:36,320
I envy that you have a mother.

14
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:39,460
And I envy that you have a great group of friends.

15
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,840
Your life should be bright

16
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,360
and full of hope.

17
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:46,680
Actually, we could have been good friends.

18
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:48,900
After all, we share the same idol.

19
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,440
I've always treated you like my own little sister.

20
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:52,759
Really.

21
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:54,440
We are not from the same world.

22
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,450
I get bullied at school.

23
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:58,120
I don't have a mom.

24
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:01,080
This auto repair shop is my only home.

25
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:03,050
Those three are my everything.

26
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:04,920
But your appearance

27
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:07,050
has indeed brought us a lot of trouble.

28
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,889
So how do you expect me to treat you?

29
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,329
Get some rest first.

30
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,040
I'm leaving.

31
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,940
Brother, it's just ahead.

32
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,040
Come.

33
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,200
Go up.

34
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,760
A bit to the left.

35
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:40,440
Left.

36
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,620
Will this be sweet?

37
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,040
Just pick it first.

38
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,060
Come on.

39
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,130
Who's there?

40
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:47,320
What are you doing?

41
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,000
Hurry.

42
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,440
Someone's coming.

43
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:49,360
Go.

44
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:51,890
Hurry up.

45
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,220
You've inspected the car.

46
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:07,440
There are absolutely no problems this time.

47
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,240
Rest assured.

48
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,200
Xiaobai.

49
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,000
What happened before

50
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,560
was indeed a bit awkward.

51
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,600
But it's fine.

52
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,040
You know what?

53
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:21,120
I really appreciated you the first time we met.

54
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,120
You're smart,

55
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:24,320
and your hands are precise and steady.

56
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,440
Don't you think

57
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,640
it's a bit of a pity to be a mechanic?

58
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,840
What happened before

59
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,560
was indeed our fault.

60
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,180
I apologize to you.

61
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,960
As for the Industrial and Commercial Bureau,

62
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,690
please help us explain to them,

63
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:38,280
so we can reopen.

64
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,480
If you have any car problems in the future,

65
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,440
you can come to me anytime.

66
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:43,440
As for the Industrial and Commercial Bureau,

67
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:45,160
you have to explain it yourselves.

68
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:48,020
Men should take responsibility for their actions.

69
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:50,040
But I really do appreciate you.

70
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:52,520
If you want to cooperate with a bigger platform in the future,

71
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,980
you can come to me anytime.

72
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,320
Yaqi.

73
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,160
Drive.

74
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,440
Boss Dong,

75
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,810
let me drive the car to the door for you.

76
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:02,760
So you are Liu Yaqi.

77
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,680
I'll do it myself.

78
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:13,400
Hai B·80608.

79
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,730
Why are you here?

80
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,159
I...

81
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,159
I came to see Bai Qing.

82
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:43,010
That's very kind of you.

83
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,540
I know you didn't do it on purpose.

84
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:45,960
It's just...

85
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,000
What do you mean it wasn't on purpose?

86
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,330
It was on purpose, okay?

87
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,360
You did it on purpose.

88
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:53,040
Do you know how much you hurt her?

89
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,080
She experienced school bullying, and you haven't.

90
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,240
So you wouldn't understand at all.

91
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:56,960
It wasn't me.

92
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:59,000
Bai Qing did it on purpose, okay?

93
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,520
Bai Qing did it on purpose?

94
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:00,920
Yes.

95
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,360
She hurt herself?

96
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:04,140
What would she gain from that?

97
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:07,640
Forget it.

98
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:09,840
Think whatever you want.

99
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:12,960
By the way.

100
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,780
I will definitely find out the truth.

101
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:17,300
Once I find out,

102
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,600
we are done.

103
00:05:56,159 --> 00:05:58,000
Mom, have some water.

104
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,560
Is there a girl

105
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:14,280
named Bai Qing in your high school?

106
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,400
There are so many students in our school.

107
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,920
How could I know everyone?

108
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,560
She is my friend.

109
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:23,960
Okay.

110
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,300
You've even made friends in high school.

111
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:28,640
Can I ask you for a favor?

112
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:31,320
Tell me, what do you want me to help you with?

113
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,409
Every grade has that one

114
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,480
poor soul who gets picked on.

115
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,880
Looks like it's a girl this year.

116
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:43,409
Is it that girl from Class 4?

117
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,760
She looks quite gentle.

118
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:45,960
Why is she so unlucky?

119
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,440
She must have provoked them.

120
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,440
Poor thing.

121
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,600
[Homeroom Teacher's Message]

122
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,000
Heaven rewards the diligent, and no one succeeds without hard work. In your studies, you have been diligent. Keep it up and become...

123
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:18,680
Heaven rewards the diligent, and no one succeeds without hard work. In your studies, you have been diligent. Keep it up and become...

124
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:35,320
Actually, she goes to the infirmary often,

125
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,200
and her injuries are quite serious.

126
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:39,000
She refuses to tell me the reason

127
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:41,159
and asks me to keep it a secret.

128
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:42,520
As for me,

129
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:45,540
I've always wanted to find a chance to chat with her.

130
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,760
Su Wan, come here for a moment.

131
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,280
You know Bai Qing, right?

132
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:54,159
I'm so sick of her pitiful look.

133
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,930
Look at how cowardly she is.

134
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,730
I've really had enough.

135
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,240
Who are you?

136
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,730
I am Bai Qing's older brother, Bai Tianyu.

137
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,600
So what?

138
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,160
Get out of my way.

139
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,120
Move it.

140
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:15,800
Ouch.

141
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,640
Am I late?

142
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:26,720
And me.

143
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,640
And me too.

144
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,280
Tell me,

145
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,960
if I send the videos of you cheating on exams,

146
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,039
bullying at school,

147
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,240
and stealing from malls

148
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:40,080
to your dad's work chat group,

149
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,080
will he still be able to keep his job?
